K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-030:134b-0: @134b 'phags pa bdud thams cad skrag par byed pa zhes bya ba /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-030:134b-1: bcom ldan 'das sh'akya thub pa la phyag 'tshal lo //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-030:134b-2: aom sarba ta th'a ga ta ma ni sha ta d'ipti /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-030:134b-4: dharma dh'a tu garbhe ma ni ma h'a ma ni /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-030:134b-5: hri da ya ma ni sv'a h'a /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-030:134b-6: sngags 'di brjod pas dkar po'i phyogs kyi lha rnams dga' zhing srung ngo //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-030:134b-7: nag po'i bdud thams cad dngang zhing brgyal lo //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-030:134b-8: dregs pa ma rungs pa rnams skrag pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-030:134b-10: bdud skrag par byed ba'i gzungs rdzogs so ////
